Services.
    - Services are used to maintain the common business logic.

    - Services Can Share the Common Business Logic to all the Controllers.

    - By using Services We Can Achieve the Code Reusability.

    - We Have Two Types Of Services.

        1.Custom Services

        2.Predefined Services


Custom Service.

    - The Services Developed By the Developer Called As Custom Services.

    - we can develop the Custom Services By using the following predefined function.

        1.provider()

        2.factory()

        3.service()

        4.value()

        5.constant()



